{"tid":2318682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國人權事務高級專員關注香港情況 指出香港的公民和政治空間急速收窄 正審視新疆有否發生嚴重違反人權的事件","createTime":"2020-12-09T13:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T16:31:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9387ba65dcdff793e7b160d710d8d0e083a4ae90","tid":2318682,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特關注港區國安法落實，影響香港基本自由。<br />\n<br />\n巴切萊特表示，關注到香港多名參與去年抗爭遊行人士被定罪，以及港區國安法落實後的情況。<br />\n<br />\n她指出香港的公民和政治空間急速收窄，對行使基本自由產生寒蟬效應。巴切萊特呼籲司法機關尊重國際義務，捍衛正當司法程序和公平審訊。<br />\n<br />\n巴切萊特亦表示，聯合國方面正審視新疆，有否發生嚴重違反人權的事件，期待明年訪問中國能夠成行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416016&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=b9e1ea4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416016&h=2077b384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416016</a>"},{"pid":"fddd3c1bc4aad46bde89a98e0294223d521ecfb3","tid":2318682,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"而家聯合國先嚟瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2aa9fa08b723aad0fd6ce8752cc23d16fac0d5","tid":2318682,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"黑狗：I'm the LAW"},{"pid":"bcd3a43e95d30ad0b0301624ba01b5e91df15f8e","tid":2318682,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c13421f0695229a4331521439ed8fddfc717c1d","tid":2318682,"uid":68111,"